## Task Management

This project uses `tkr` for task management. Tickets are stored as Markdown files
in `.tkr/tickets/`.

- Get next task: `tkr next --plain`
- Show task: `tkr show <id> --plain`
- Claim task: `tkr claim <id>`
- Complete task: `tkr done <id>`
- List tasks: `tkr list --plain`
- Always reference ticket IDs in commits: `feat({{.Prefix}}-N): description`
